  "body": "\r\n\r\n**Is this a bug report or feature request?**\r\n* Bug Report\r\n\r\n**Deviation from expected behavior:**\r\nUsing credentials provided by the obc, the application can able to create a new bucket in the object store\r\n**Expected behavior:**\r\nThe application should only access the bucket provided by the obc\r\n\r\n**How to reproduce it (minimal and precise):**\r\nKubectl create -f <path to obc>\r\n\r\nUsing the access credentials from a secret, create bucket via s3cmd or awscli\r\n\r\n**Environment**:\r\nminikube with latest rook and ceph v14.2.4 images\r\n\r\n**Solution**\r\nThe user who got created by the provisioner during obc creation need to be restricted via user policies\r\n\r\n",
